<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Aegis Safety Consultancy | Perth, Western Australia</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Karla:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0c1a2e;
    --navy-mid: #162640;
    --navy-light: #1e3555;
    --amber: #e8951a;
    --amber-light: #f5a930;
    --offwhite: #f4efe6;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --gray: #8a9ab5;
    --gray-light: #c8d3e6;
    --text-dark: #0c1a2e;
    --text-body: #2c3e55;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Karla', sans-serif;
    background: var(--offwhite);
    color: var(--text-body);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ---- NAV ---- */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(12, 26, 46, 0.97);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--amber);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 48px; height: 68px;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    display: flex; align-items: center;
  }
  .nav-logo img { height: 44px; width: auto; display: block; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--gray-light); text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--amber); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--amber); color: var(--navy);
    padding: 9px 22px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--amber-light); }

  /* ---- HERO ---- */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--navy);
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    padding: 120px 48px 80px;
  }
  .hero-grid-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(232,149,26,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(232,149,26,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }
  .hero-glow {
    position: absolute; top: -200px; right: -200px;
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,149,26,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-content { position: relative; max-width: 800px; }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(232,149,26,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(232,149,26,0.3);
    color: var(--amber); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .hero-tag::before { content: ''; width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--amber); border-radius: 50%; display: block; }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(52px, 7vw, 92px);
    font-weight: 800; line-height: 0.95;
    color: var(--white); text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  h1 em { color: var(--amber); font-style: normal; }
  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-light); max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--amber); color: var(--navy);
    padding: 15px 32px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.2s; display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--amber-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-outline {
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25); color: var(--white);
    padding: 13px 32px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.2s; display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--amber); color: var(--amber); }

  /* ---- SECTION SHARED ---- */
  section { padding: 96px 48px; }
  .section-tag {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--amber); margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 58px); font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .lead {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.75;
    color: #4a6080; max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  /* ---- SERVICES ---- */
  #services { background: var(--white); }
  .services-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .service-card {
    background: var(--offwhite); padding: 36px 32px;
    border-left: 4px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .service-card::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; right: 0;
    width: 80px; height: 80px;
    background: rgba(232,149,26,0.06);
    border-radius: 50% 0 0 0;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .service-card:hover { background: var(--navy); border-left-color: var(--amber); }
  .service-card:hover .service-icon { color: var(--amber); }
  .service-card:hover .service-title { color: var(--white); }
  .service-card:hover .service-desc { color: var(--gray); }
  .service-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .service-title {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--navy);
    transition: color 0.25s;
  }
  .service-desc { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; color: #5a7090; transition: color 0.25s; }

  /* ---- REMOTE SUPPORT ---- */
  #remote {
    background: var(--navy);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center;
  }
  #remote h2, #remote .section-tag { color: var(--white); }
  #remote h2 em { color: var(--amber); font-style: normal; }
  #remote .lead { color: var(--gray); }
  .remote-card {
    background: var(--navy-light); border: 1px solid rgba(232,149,26,0.2);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 40px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .remote-card::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--amber), var(--amber-light));
  }
  .remote-features { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .remote-features li {
    color: var(--gray-light); font-size: 14px; padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;
  }
  .remote-features li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--amber); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

  /* ---- SECTORS ---- */
  #sectors { background: var(--offwhite); }
  .sectors-grid {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .sector-pill {
    background: var(--white); border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-light);
    padding: 10px 22px; border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--navy);
    transition: all 0.2s; cursor: default;
  }
  .sector-pill:hover { background: var(--navy); color: var(--amber); border-color: var(--navy); }

  /* ---- CONTACT ---- */
  #contact { background: var(--offwhite); }
  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; }
  .contact-form-wrap {
    background: var(--white); border-radius: 8px; padding: 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-light); box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  label { display: block; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 7px; }
  input, textarea, select {
    width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-light);
    border-radius: 4px; font-family: 'Karla', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-body); background: var(--offwhite);
    transition: border-color 0.2s; outline: none;
  }
  input:focus, textarea:focus, select:focus { border-color: var(--amber); background: var(--white); }
  textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 120px; }
  .contact-info { padding-top: 8px; }
  .contact-info h3 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .contact-info p { font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #4a6080; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .contact-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
  .contact-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; }
  .contact-item-icon {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--navy); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .contact-item-text strong { display: block; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .contact-item-text p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--navy); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ---- FOOTER ---- */
  footer {
    background: var(--navy); padding: 40px 48px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--amber);
  }
  .footer-left {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .footer-left span { color: var(--amber); }
  footer p { color: var(--gray); font-size: 13px; }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
  .footer-links a { color: var(--gray); text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--amber); }

  /* ---- ANIMATIONS ---- */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .hero-tag { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; }
  h1 { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.1s ease both; }
  .hero-sub { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.2s ease both; }
  .hero-actions { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.3s ease both; }

  /* ---- RESPONSIVE ---- */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 0 24px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    section { padding: 72px 24px; }
    #hero { padding: 100px 24px 64px; }
    #remote, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .footer-links { justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Aegis Safety Consultancy"/>
  </div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="#remote">Remote Support</a></li>
    <li><a href="#sectors">Industries</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Get in Touch</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-tag">Perth, Western Australia</div>
    <h1>Practical Safety.<br/><em>Without the</em><br/>Overhead.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Expert WHS consulting for construction, mining, and trades businesses — without the cost of a full-time hire. Simple, no-nonsense safety support when and where you need it.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#remote" class="btn-primary">See Remote Support</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-outline">Talk to Matt</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section id="services">
  <div class="section-tag">What We Do</div>
  <h2>Safety Services<br/>That Actually Get Used</h2>
  <p class="lead">No overcomplicated processes. Workers follow the path of least resistance — safety processes need to be clear and simple, and the rest will follow.</p>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">🔍</div>
      <div class="service-title">Risk Assessments</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Thorough, site-specific risk assessments that identify real hazards and set clear, actionable controls.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">📋</div>
      <div class="service-title">Safe Work Method Statements</div>
      <div class="service-desc">SWMS written in plain language — compliant, practical, and actually understood by the workers using them.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">🏗️</div>
      <div class="service-title">Safety Management Systems</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Build or overhaul your SMS from the ground up. Systems that work in the real world, not just on paper.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">📁</div>
      <div class="service-title">Safety Documentation</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Policies, procedures, plans, templates — professionally written documentation tailored to your business.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">🔎</div>
      <div class="service-title">Incident Investigations</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Structured incident investigations that find root causes, not just blame — and prevent recurrence.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">✅</div>
      <div class="service-title">Audits & Compliance</div>
      <div class="service-desc">WHS legislation compliance audits with clear findings and prioritised corrective action plans.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">📊</div>
      <div class="service-title">Safety Data Analysis</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Turn your incident data and leading indicators into insights that actually drive performance improvement.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">🌐</div>
      <div class="service-title">Remote Safety Support</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Full HSE support delivered remotely — phone, email, and documentation — without the full-time wage.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- REMOTE SUPPORT -->
<section id="remote">
  <div>
    <div class="section-tag">Our Flagship Offer</div>
    <h2>HSE Support.<br/><em>No Full-Time</em><br/>Hire Required.</h2>
    <p class="lead">Smaller businesses shouldn't have to choose between proper safety support and staying profitable. Our remote support plan gives you a dedicated safety consultant in your corner — for less than a day's wages.</p>
    <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7;">Available 24/7 by phone and email. We respond when you need us — not during office hours. Whether it's a quick compliance question, a critical incident, or a tight deadline on documentation, we're there.</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <div class="remote-card">
      <ul class="remote-features">
        <li>24/7 phone and email access to your consultant</li>
        <li>Unlimited safety questions and compliance guidance</li>
        <li>WHS legislation advice specific to WA</li>
        <li>Priority response for incidents and urgent matters</li>
        <li>Monthly check-in call</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary" style="width:100%; text-align:center; display:block;">Start Remote Support →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTORS -->
<section id="sectors">
  <div class="section-tag">Industries We Serve</div>
  <h2>Built for<br/>Blue-Collar Business</h2>
  <p class="lead">We work across the high-hazard industries that keep Western Australia running. If your people work with their hands, we know your risks.</p>
  <div class="sectors-grid">
    <div class="sector-pill">⚒️ Construction</div>
    <div class="sector-pill">⛏️ Mining</div>
    <div class="sector-pill">🏭 Manufacturing</div>
    <div class="sector-pill">🔧 Workshops</div>
    <div class="sector-pill">🏗️ Refineries</div>
    <div class="sector-pill">🪖 Defence</div>
    <div class="sector-pill">🔩 Trades</div>
    <div class="sector-pill">⚙️ Heavy Industry</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT -->
