  <h2>Let's Talk Safety</h2>
  <div class="contact-grid" style="margin-top:48px;">
    <div class="contact-form-wrap">
      <div style="margin-bottom:24px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Lora',serif; color:#4a6080; line-height:1.7;">Tell us about your business and what you need. We'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
